        <div></div>
    </p><table class="">
        <tbody>
            <tr>
                <td>
                    <img width="200" src="//wow.zamimg.com/images/hearthstone/cards/enus/medium/NEW1_037.png?9577" class="hearthhead-tooltip-image">
                    @*<table><tbody><tr><td><span class="q"><i>He's currently trying to craft a "flail-axe", but all the other swordsmiths say it can't be done.</i></span></td><th style="background-position:right top"></th></tr><tr class="hearthhead-tooltip-inner"><th style="background-position:left bottom"></th><th style="background-position:right bottom"></th></tr></tbody></table>*@
